metadata.name: Cage of time
metadata.description:
This artwork portrays the character in the form of bold, raw strokes and warm colours and mirrors his rage, pain and adversities that he endures in his life. 

It depicts the overlap of the past with the present. Frames within frames in the artwork express how the protagonist is trapped in the circumstances from which he can’t escape.

This surreal work is also inspired by Salvador Dali. It indicates that time always flows.
It’s superior than human life.
The time keeps ticking.
It comes back in flashes no matter how fast you run. 
Time is a traitor, sloppy and viscous.
Time is a disease, lying around the universe.

No of souls: 1
